:"2017-07-26T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻牆好似無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb8f95e6f1c39ceee94afe19104975810937fe1","tid":336083,"uid":70060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4be51afbe6bf4c963850d3c45a8efb069b3e634f","tid":336083,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐到底有冇人搵到條法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6871545aa272ae9524d87b638df4eeec62c75592","tid":336083,"uid":39750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實佢冇乜錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係sim卡個邊以偏蓋全，好似得移動聯通係可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他就算翻牆，大陸從來都冇一條法律係話唔俾翻牆<br />\n即使上次撞上翻牆公司逼佢收皮<br />\n都冇清楚解釋佢犯左邊條例，只係直接要佢收皮</blockquote><br />\n大陸有條法例寫到明，要用官方線路接入國際互聯網，用VPN、proxy之類翻墻已經唔係用官方線路，翻墻絕對犯法</blockquote><br />\n邊個章節既法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n咁違者有乜後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n好似得重慶有明文禁止<br />\n 不以盈利為目的，初次實施上述違法行為，責令停止聯網，給予警告。"},{"pid":"0c32709cd17845cf767b96ba28a7473601a82241","tid":336083,"uid":88183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"佢痴q左線.jpg"},{"pid":"40e7fc0cb0f4aebeefa7cfddae13dd075fb582bd","tid":336083,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"官喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74a40ad72422f135fb8c28a302fc2820de0127a","tid":336083,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d28265bc33ab78e5ffd11a9292a485b2f0fa2995","tid":336083,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfeb14ca5949c70b7f674dcc70c6d6814ba36bbb","tid":336083,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實佢冇乜錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係sim卡個邊以偏蓋全，好似得移動聯通係可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他就算翻牆，大陸從來都冇一條法律係話唔俾翻牆<br />\n即使上次撞上翻牆公司逼佢收皮<br />\n都冇清楚解釋佢犯左邊條例，只係直接要佢收皮</blockquote><br />\n大陸有條法例寫到明，要用官方線路接入國際互聯網，用VPN、proxy之類翻墻已經唔係用官方線路，翻墻絕對犯法</blockquote><br />\n邊個章節既法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n咁違者有乜後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n2017 年一月，中國工業和信息化部發文監管虛擬私人網路絡 (VPN)「翻牆」的灰色地帶。而在 2017 年 3 月 27 日，中國直轄市之一的重慶，發布了新的《重慶市公安機關網絡監管行政處罰裁量基準》修訂版，規定在重慶司法管轄區的人使用網絡翻牆工具翻越中國當局設置的資訊封鎖牆訪問牆外網站的人可以被處以罰款，「構成犯罪的，依法追究刑事責任」。<br />\n<br />\n處罰措施<br />\n<br />\n不以盈利為目的，初次實施上述違法行為，責令停止聯網，給予警告。<br />\n<br />\n以盈利為目的實施上述違法行為，違法所得在 5,000 元（約台幣 25000 元）以下的，責令停止聯網，給予警告，同時沒收違法所得；以盈利為目的實施上述違法行為，違法所得在人民幣 5,000 元 (約台幣 25000 元) 以上 10,000 元 (約台幣 50000 元) 以下的，責令停止聯網，給予警告，對個人可以並處 5,000 元 (約台幣 25000 元) 以下罰款，對單位處以 5,000 元 (約台幣 25000 元) 以上 10,000 元 (約台幣 50000 元) 以下罰款，同時沒收違法所得。」"},{"pid":"9937b792a44d08d5da19ebc1a551dec7f9d5793d","tid":336083,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑到急屎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0cf48390a9cfb0b3ca5a2f0243e993bc494c619f","tid":336083,"uid":8794,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"佢答得好圓滑喎<br />\n<br />\n有啲vpn係官方認可 有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n盲反就係呢啲 襯暑假引成班小學雞出黎正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591bfc669dd7bedff2ab24bcc6e5691df8920a80","tid":336083,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"原片好笑啲，岩岩嗰段已經cut 過黎"},{"pid":"d9b653d2179bc9741c04524eeb64946e68b3beb5","tid":336083,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"真係on99, 一啲政治智慧都無，喺街求其捉個mk仔都分分鐘識講嘢過依班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dd3f51edd252ade2ea2f83b3339b9d288267ba","tid":336083,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06888ef7de1d4093a610fda0ac00c3aa37cb2d0","tid":336083,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d7a48ac74804e31b993b9a820385524c3ab9867","tid":336083,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢答得好圓滑喎<br />\n<br />\n有啲vpn係官方認可 有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n盲反就係呢啲 襯暑假引成班小學雞出黎正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a742027487337108d4bef3eea5b069a6fe5f64e2","tid":336083,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冚家死撚左佢去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efe76c4b57debfaa85d5dcf98dd537b5c48732c","tid":336083,"uid":4571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s