e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"睇到o撚哂嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff6c91e30304be24845cd90eb174cb568da5cec","tid":336083,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢答得好圓滑喎<br />\n<br />\n有啲vpn係官方認可 有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n盲反就係呢啲 襯暑假引成班小學雞出黎正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人(十幾歲嘅)睇呢段嘢會覺得佢智障<br />\n但你試下畀大陸人睇，應該會一嘢get到香港人嗰種「傲慢」<br />\n根本就係恥笑緊呢個地方連上個網都冇自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平心而論佢哋其實算係老實，都冇點用官腔遊花園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a66847538653d30db77a1ceee3c8537631ff8f","tid":336083,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"佢好人好姐做乜翻牆<br />\n陳局長上到去係唔係睇D中共唔想你睇既網, 咁大逆不道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1fac9ee2e797f286b27a472903a5224a28b4ae","tid":336083,"uid":2707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢好人好姐做乜翻牆<br />\n陳局長上到去係唔係睇D中共唔想你睇既網, 咁大逆不道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咪答咗你囉<br />\n唔翻牆連自己啲業務嘢分分鐘都睇唔到<br />\n中共搞啲好多外國人到嘅大型會議都要面對呢類問題<br />\n而唔係你哋想像嘅咩嘢六四資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(應該答得太認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ac1be90563cbc1d0692876dbc9be4f6bc11dbed5","tid":336083,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"食左誠實豆豆包"},{"pid":"7801866821e2e33eb760d641648a773c36115746","tid":336083,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"