quote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傲咩慢... 下一句係咪要包容"},{"pid":"6813cd7bb364ef1cfc0c88cfbd0d706bb400c38d","tid":336083,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 連登真係多五毛 翻牆都有人撐"},{"pid":"73d8b5bcbf5b96d7e13296c25b2d58bcdd5e67e5","tid":336083,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94ac37f30298d84659a2ca377c293d1eaa079d34","tid":336083,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9a5f1ed167c6a59a90e3553c269da2785991a2","tid":336083,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻牆好似無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無🤔咁強國封vpn係咩原因？"},{"pid":"c1f9ed17b155809a9fe38b9cb261753661368e47","tid":336083,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>翻牆好似無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無🤔咁強國封vpn係咩原因？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果要因為翻牆犯法上門拉人<br />\n會耗費巨量警力🤔"},{"pid":"c8ffac9d2d41d658309cf1c5ffe13aa9bd3e4f12","tid":336083,"uid":62969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:34:58.000Z","msg":"之後仲會唔會見到個局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662a7e08cd132a913523be428207f7b47d6e2676","tid":336083,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:34:26.000Z","msg":"局長教你如何與黨唱反調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dc802ef037a164d89fae5a371ea48651746f08","tid":336083,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:43:07.000Z","msg":